desc_long								关于这款游戏							Simple Spy is a dynamic and minimalist 2d platformer. Though Simple Spy is a minimalist platformer,you can also find all fun and essence needed for a full fledged platformer. everything in Simple Spy is achieved through a combination of three action such as running,jumping and rolling.the main focus of the game is simplicity  with hard core gameplay and unique game features and obstacles.featuresExplore 75 levels and 5 bonus levels6 different character with unique animation to unlockChallenging gameplay based on color changing platform.Minimalist Levels but Hardcore gameplay						
